headline: Generac Promotes Jim Barnes to Executive Vice President - Global Supply Chain
summary: Generac Holdings Inc. (NYSE: GNRC), a leading global designer, manufacturer and provider of energy technology solutions and other power products, today announced the promotion of Jim Barnes to Executive Vice President – Global Supply Chain.
